## ðŸ’¡ Dynamic Module UI Rendering (Frontend)

### `dashboard/page.tsx`

```tsx
const modules = await fetch('/api/modules').then(res => res.json())

return (
  <div>
    {modules.includes('admissions') && <Admissions />}
    {modules.includes('courses') && <Courses />}
    {modules.includes('ai') && <AIChatbot />}
  </div>
)
```

